sequenceDiagram
  participant A as Admin Web
  participant B as Backend API
  participant M as Android Client
  participant R as GBCR/RCLR
  A->>B: Publish schema v2
  M->>R: Select answer on schema v1
  M->>B: PATCH answers(clientVersion=v1)
  B->>R: Compare old DAG v1 with current DAG v2
  alt answers map cleanly
    R-->>B: atomic_recovery
    B-->>M: preserved answers + v2 schema
  else visible path removed or orphan created
    R-->>B: RCLR_ROLLBACK / RCLR_CONFLICT
    B-->>M: stable node + sanitized answers
  end
  M->>R: Re-render valid visible path
